name: BatonRougeGuide
0:
”Alexa, open Baton Rouge Guide”
”tell me the top five things”
”tell me a good attraction”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: baton rouge guide
des:
This is a fully fledged trip advisor for the capital city of Louisiana: Baton Rouge.

This beautiful city boasts several points of interest that everyone can enjoy. Explore the past, present, and future of the city and have fun with friends, either getting scared at haunted plantations or enjoying life at world famous breweries. 

For any additional information, do not hesitate on visiting

VisitBatonRouge.com

Enjoy!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
